{"tid":1836270,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"09年豬流感酒店全棟隔離  應變級別由「嚴重」提升至「緊急」","createTime":"2020-01-23T06:51:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T15:23:47.000Z","uid":37554,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a6923868b22ebd58d3cf75411f45bd45975aff03","tid":1836270,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T06:51:34.000Z","msg":"2009年香港爆發豬流感(甲型H1N1流感)，一名墨西哥男子帶病來港，入住灣仔維景酒店，同樣為中旅集團旗下的四星級酒店。男子翌日便入院，政府即時封鎖事發酒店，所有旅客及員工需接受隔離，一星期後方解封，酒店隔離事件後來更被改編為電視劇集。<br />\n<br />\n由於香港大學與衞生署近日開始研發新的檢測試驗，所以在今晚八時能夠確診這位病人是患上人類豬流感，亦即是世界衞生組織最近改名為A型H1N1流感。<br />\n由於香港有第一個確診個案，我們今晚亦在行政長官接受衞生署署長的建議下，把香港的應變級別由「嚴重」提升至「緊急」的最高級別。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C1BodZGoo8Q&amp;feature\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DC1BodZGoo8Q%26feature&d=BfE6afXCHr80cM3PNjd%2Fp%2FjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=fa6c1cbb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=C1BodZGoo8Q&amp;feature</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ff9f64b373eacb26af8b7a278c88ee5b629c5bd","tid":1836270,"uid":28223,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T06:54:26.000Z","msg":"隔離7日情??"},{"pid":"e911c9ab4d4010db212b4a398ff51fe0e44c4904","tid":1836270,"uid":99307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T07:01:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e00f3b7754572cebe99138e92ad1ac5dac4d6db9","tid":1836270,"uid":239525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T07:03:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b5756867aece78d90932d9d7a4c7eb1b967530c","tid":1836270,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T11:39:04.000Z","msg":"yeah, I remember this... we acted quick on this back in 2009 tho. This time around? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"229054e55c1449b8a06e282f62e0